1
00:00:16,320 --> 00:00:17,320
That's crossing the line.

2
00:00:17,680 --> 00:00:18,680
Oh.

3
00:00:19,490 --> 00:00:20,490
Sorry.

4
00:00:22,220 --> 00:00:23,220
Forget it.

5
00:00:23,590 --> 00:00:24,420
You should just go home for today.

6
00:00:24,420 --> 00:00:25,420
Huh?

7
00:00:25,490 --> 00:00:26,360
A guy from another school...

8
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:27,360
...sneaking into an all-girls' school...

9
00:00:27,830 --> 00:00:28,630
...and doing something like this.

10
00:00:28,630 --> 00:00:29,960
It'll be a disaster if you get caught.

11
00:00:30,160 --> 00:00:31,260
You should really go.

12
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:59,760
I'm sorry...

13
00:01:06,030 --> 00:01:07,100
From that moment on...

14
00:01:07,100 --> 00:01:09,040
I made a vow
to never trust anyone again.

15
00:01:09,040 --> 00:01:10,070
The moment I decided that,

16
00:01:10,100 --> 00:01:11,240
the idea of falling for someone...

17
00:01:11,240 --> 00:01:12,270
...became impossible for me.

18
00:01:12,640 --> 00:01:14,540
The thought that I'd just
end up getting betrayed anyway...

19
00:01:14,540 --> 00:01:15,910
...made letting anyone in...

20
00:01:15,910 --> 00:01:17,480
...so terrifying
I couldn't bring myself to do it.

21
00:01:17,740 --> 00:01:18,740
Never again...

22
00:01:19,850 --> 00:01:21,550
...will I fall for anyone.

23
00:01:21,550 --> 00:01:22,720
I'll never trust again.

24
00:01:23,850 --> 00:01:25,990
I will never,
ever forgive you.

25
00:01:27,490 --> 00:01:29,290
I mean it this time.
